{"tid":2033470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"簡易自製VPN教學","createTime":"2020-05-24T16:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T13:18:34.000Z","uid":26414,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"097b15d2422f1788e66f0edca8efe5b72edf9013","tid":2033470,"uid":26414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"呢個係我之前教支那反賊嘅教學，大家可以參考下，我呢個係儘量簡單，所以冇寫反向代理、https加密<br />\n<br />\n一個親自搭建的VPN，能夠有效保護自己的個人私隱，而且可以有效減少被自殺的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n購買vps(虛擬服務器)的問題暫且放開一邊，因為這個隨便google都可以找得到，只要注意不要使用中國的主機供應商提供的vps即可。實在沒有錢的，也可以使用(白嫖)google提供的 谷歌雲（GPC)，谷歌雲 可以提供300美金的一年體驗券。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ty2D35r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTy2D35r.png&h=bc716691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買好VPS後，先下載Termius(mac、windows、iOS 、Android)，然後你可以在你購買VPS的地方得到你的IP地址、密碼<br />\n<br />\ntermius下載連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://termius.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftermius.com%2F&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=344bd460\" target=\"_blank\">https://termius.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA15J5Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA15J5Y.png&h=5292f518&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jE5BQLY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjE5BQLY.png&h=f0dcdf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kw9rjj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kw9rjj.png&h=f28ea62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n直接copy下面腳本<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">bash &lt;(curl -s -L https://git.io/v2ray.sh)</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKy7XrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKy7XrJ.png&h=c3041d62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxaVmTp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxaVmTp.png&h=216c6181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次連接你的vps時，直接輸入v2ray<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nyi7XrK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyi7XrK.png&h=2bab9389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5PKZFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5PKZFk.png&h=07b81f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51307a4bf9645a79a8cad4c0d68aef8058a458c9","tid":2033470,"uid":26414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"至於連接，就用呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVwxo8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVwxo8e.png&h=e69b49fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHVY38e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHVY38e.png&h=9a3f608b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用生成嘅二維碼掃一掃就搞掂"},{"pid":"e3312734b0233caaa44119fc8177da2128bb8971","tid":2033470,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"How much<br />\n利申 冇錢"},{"pid":"02e2661502de0c201fd3ef11a18ac49b75bd6262","tid":2033470,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ff3935e6b6a13bd9f281304be2ddfdb81a24d5c","tid":2033470,"uid":26414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3312734b0233caaa44119fc8177da2128bb8971","tid":2033470,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"How much<br />\n利申 冇錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"我展示用嘅係vultr，5蚊美金一個月<br />\n俄羅斯嘅vps幾蚊一個月都有，好似叫伯力<br />\n有間美國嘅1美國一個月都有<br />\n想唔洗錢就用google ，上面講左"},{"pid":"fe386a822fe9ee7f26c1567827d25beb58ca46a9","tid":2033470,"uid":26414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e2661502de0c201fd3ef11a18ac49b75bd6262","tid":2033470,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"此回